snippet.title: Take the Dream IX Steam Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
GREENLIGHT PAGE: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=542809450
Appreciate those who vote, game will come out on a variety of indie game sites for free on Halloween, and onto Steam if it goes through Greenlight when it does. Appreciate anyone who may support my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/AestheticGamer
